My Personal Toolkit ***********************************************************
This repo will include all the stuff use I while kicking off a project

Contents-----------------------------------------------------------------------

folders >

styles
scripts
images
includes
backup

files >

index.php- doctype, title, link to style.css, script.js, jquery.js, icon.png
	   and html5 shim
style.css-  contains reset.css and additional custom start off styles
	    reset from http://meyerweb.com/eric/tools/css/reset/
grid.css-  custom grid
script.js-  contains just a $(document).ready(function(){}); line
jquery.js- current version of jquery
icon.png- a black 64x64 png file
.htaccess- for the directory index, the error documents, directory listing 
	   options and denying access to the .htaccess file itself.
	   from http://www.csskarma.com/blog/creating-an-htaccess-template/
robots.txt- defining access for web crawlers and robots
sitemap.xml- list of pages for crawlers and users
404.php- error document for files that were not found
403.php- error document for forbidden files
500.php- error document for unknown errors
